			<common:generalComment xml:lang="en">Water disinfectant is used in emergency situations where regular water service is interrupted. It helps in making water safer to drink by killing or removing germs to a safe level. It can be in the form of unscented household chlorine bleach, iodine, or chlorine dioxide tablets. It is also used for disinfecting surfaces by killing viruses and bacteria.</common:generalComment>
			<common:generalComment xml:lang="zh">水消毒剂用于常规供水服务中断的紧急情况。它可以杀死或清除水中的病菌，使其达到安全水平，从而使饮用水更安全。它可以是无味家用氯漂白剂、碘或二氧化氯片剂。它还可以杀死病毒和细菌，用于表面消毒。</common:generalComment>
